data.description: Welcome to the Village at Union Mills.  This lovingly cared for home is situated near the end of a quiet Tree-lined street.   Light and bright, this home has many  features accentuating it’s charm.  There is a gas fireplace in the living room, a breakfast nook in kitchen filled with natural light and French doors leading to a covered porch.  And French doors off a bedroom, leading to a private patio – with perfect spot for a hot tub.  This remodeled home has new A/C, a new roof, new hot water heater.  The 2 car garage is accessed from alley. Convenient location near the JBLM, I-5, businesses & shopping.  GREAT INVESTMENT!  The owner of this home has a steady stream of referrals from JBLM for use as an Air B&B.
